data.text:
Syrian men carry the coffin of late filmmaker Moustapha Akkad to al-Rawdah Mosque in Aleppo, Syria, Sunday, Nov. 13, 2005. Akkad, Syrian-born producer of the "Halloween" horror film series died Friday from wounds sustained in a hotel bombing in Amman, Jordan and was laid to rest Sunday. (AP Photo/ Bassem Tellawi)
